This tool offers businesses a seamless and efficient way to conduct transactions with their clients.
The PayPal Direct Shopping Link Generator For Business 2 enables companies to customize payment links,
tailoring them to specific products, services, or invoice amounts. This level of personalization ensures
a smooth and professional payment experience for both parties involved.

Moreover, the use of email as a medium for sending payment links provides added convenience for businesses
and their customers alike. Companies can easily integrate payment links into their existing email templates
or use them as standalone messages.

1 - Generate the link
2 - Send the link with images and text to your contacts.

Note:
The link goes to Paypal.com and let users enter credit card details to finish the purchase.
Also can define/customize success payment page and fail payment page.

